parameters: Thief Nora: I found her, she's right here!

Priestess Sophia: Your complexion doesn't look good. Is
there something wrong with your body?

Master Thief Perno: I can only do half-hearted disguises
because my magic is unstable...

Master Thief Perno: Moreover, today we need to go to a
dangerous place. Does anyone here know the whereabouts of
the magical beasts' lair?

Mage Relm: I've heard rumors that it's a place where even
the imperial army, ruled by orcs, doesn't dare to
intervene.

Master Thief Perno: It seems that my great-grandfather
stole it to make fun of the warriors of Valt and the orcs,
because he was mischievous.
Mage Relm: You're quite an extraordinary person...

Master Thief Perno: It was written that my father tried to
return it relying on the records, but he gave up due to the
sharp sense of smell possessed by the orcs.

Clea: I would like to engage in combat, but I suppose such
actions are prohibited this time as well, right?

Master Thief Perno: The rules demanded by the voice have
become stricter.

Master Thief Perno: It's absolutely impossible for me
alone... There are two more places left... I want you to
cooperate until the end.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

\CL Area Liberation\c[18]\CL Valt Region / Lair of Magical
